I've received VERY FEW registrations for Smarty.
I don't know the reason. I think that the register fee is very
reasonable, and I find that Smarty is really usefull (at least
to me :-).
If you don't like this program for any reason, or is not usefull
to you because it lacks a certain feature, please just tell me so !

Thanks !

@ENDNODE

